{"tid":177704,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"仲翻緊學嘅你哋平時帶啲咩錶","createTime":"2017-03-29T04:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T07:08:27.000Z","uid":57739,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2acdafe4a93b122bdf1b8605f46edbb5dbd11283","tid":177704,"uid":57739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/124326_33548780c43cf3868f3a7da29ec7cdc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F124326_33548780c43cf3868f3a7da29ec7cdc2.jpg&h=3e6c1bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時翻學做運動冇乜特別嘢嘅話<br />\n多數帶apple watch<br />\n幾鐘意佢外形 又唔太貴<br />\n不過成日要叉電其實有啲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S198GS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS198GS4.jpg&h=f92cf415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時出街會帶<br />\n其實中意黑藍圈GMT-Master II多啲<br />\n好似後生啲咁<br />\n不過冇咁多錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n翻緊學嘅巴打們帶啲咩錶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s. 近排想買隻新<br />\n巴打有冇budget10k-20k樓下<br />\n帶上手幾好睇同幾後生嘅錶推介?"},{"pid":"de36034464ca1bb8126c08b4f16753d4e1f57f16","tid":177704,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"又曬命，做我ＳＰ好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f3077d20871511c3cfd0e34fde786275ea88fa","tid":177704,"uid":57739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又曬命，做我ＳＰ好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇曬命囉 呢到勁多巴打有好多靚錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPM me la sp就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9631f41fbb95d634e4d5475665cec7666e780499",